originalText.text: I absolutely love this school. I attended this school back in 2009. I graduated 2010. This school gave me the push and the fighting chance I needed to succeed. The teachers are amazing, and actually want to help you and see you win. I will never forget my experience at West Side. I made long term friends and long term memories.

originalText.text: west side is a great school, the greatest thing about it is the faculty. Now most schools are just schools where kids go, go to class and cannot wait to get out,and they can have alot of resources, but without exceptional staff thats all they are, just some school. west side is not like that, believe me i was probably much more skeptical than alot of people, and honestly it was a mistake that i ended up there in the first place, but it is true some of the teachers there at west side are some of the most compassionate, not just teachers but they are some of the most compassionate people i have ever met. The teachers there they will help you, but only if you want to be helped, if you are serious about finishing high school, they will help you, they will work with you, and they will advise you if you need it. west side high school is a place for people who need a second chance its not just some transfer school, i legitimately met some really smart and interesting people there, we all had just gone down the wrong path, made some bad choices, and west side helped us get back to a place where we can actually have a decent future.
